headline: What You Need to Know Before NXP Semiconductors Q4 2025 Earnings
summary: NXP Semiconductors (NASDAQ: NXPI) reports Q4 2025 earnings today after market close at 4:10 PM ET. Wall Street expects earnings of $3.31 per share on revenue of $3.30 billion, representing 4.1% year-over-year EPS growth and 6.1% revenue growth.
